.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
\&\fIPlBar\fR will calculate all of the geodesy-normalized Legendre polynomials up to degree \s-1LMAX\s0 for a given argument. These are calculated using a standard three-term recursion formula. The integral of the geodesy-normalized Legendre polynomials over the interval [\-1, 1] is 2.
