An array of geodesy-normalized Legendre polynomials up to degree \s-1LMAX\s0. Degree L corresponds to array index L+1.
.IP "\s-1LMAX\s0" 10
.IX Item "LMAX"
(input) \s-1INTEGER\s0
.Sp
The maximum degree of the Legendre polynomials to be computed.
